##  CRAFT Breakdown

| **Layer** | **What It Means**        | **Implementation**                                                                 |
|-----------|--------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **C**     | **Clear Command**        | Every script has clear entry points, file paths, and comments                      |
| **R**     | **Robust Reasoning**     | Admin checks, module validation, failure exits all in place                        |
| **A**     | **Automation Friendly**  | Logs, colours, emoji, and CLI+CSV+HTML output                                      |
| **F**     | **Failsafe Design**      | No destructive commands, all read-only unless explicitly chosen                    |
| **T**     | **Testable Templates**   | Modularised with `lib`, `requirements`, `Makefile.ps1` — CI/CD ready               |


